				remembered when I was 14 I created a really simple website (not live
				just in my PC) with HTML and notepad!. It was really fun. I showed it to
				all my friends and family.
			</p>
		</Section>
		<Section title="blogs" more="See all blogs">
			<p>
				Hello! My name is Mohammadreza Hamzehei and I'm a front-end web
